Package edu.phema.elm_to_omop.helper

Class Config

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.phema.elm_to_omop.helper.Config
  • public final class Config
extends Object
    This class sets the configuration information. It looks first for command line arguments. If not present, then pulls them from configuration file. Config file is must be located in the config directory and named config.properties.

    • Constructor Summary
